interaction, with <!-- l. 512 --><math display='inline' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML'><mrow><mi>a</mi> <mo class='MathClass-rel' stretchy='false'>=</mo> <mn>0.1</mn></mrow></math>
in the article’s examples. Of course, this model is very simple; it can be complexified <span class='cmti-10x-x-109'>ad
